• Quilted inner layer.

Welt hand pockets.
Machine wash/dry.

description:
The refrigerator section offers ample space for storing fresh produce, beverages, dairy products, and other perishable items. It typically includes adjustable shelves, door bins, and drawers to help you organize your food items efficiently. The shelves can be customized to accommodate taller items, and the door bins are designed to hold condiments, bottles, and smaller items.

 

The freezer section of the refrigerator provides plenty of room for frozen foods such as meats, vegetables, ice cream, and pre-prepared meals. It often features multiple shelves and drawers to help you keep the freezer organized and easily access your frozen items.

 

The 528-liter capacity means that this refrigerator can store a significant amount of food and beverages, making it suitable for larger households or individuals who prefer to do bulk shopping. The side-by-side design also offers the advantage of having both the refrigerator and freezer compartments at eye level, making it convenient to access frequently used items without bending down.

short_specifications: A colloquial refrigerator is a commercial and home appliance consisting of a thermally insulated compartment and a heat pump (mechanical, electronic or chemical) that transfers heat from its inside to its external environment so that its inside is cooled to a temperature below the room temperature.

description:
The refrigerator section offers ample space for storing fresh produce, beverages, dairy products, and other perishable items. It typically includes adjustable shelves, door bins, and drawers to help you organize your food items efficiently. The shelves can be customized to accommodate taller items, and the door bins are designed to hold condiments, bottles, and smaller items.

 

The freezer section of the refrigerator provides plenty of room for frozen foods such as meats, vegetables, ice cream, and pre-prepared meals. It often features multiple shelves and drawers to help you keep the freezer organized and easily access your frozen items.

 

The 528-liter capacity means that this refrigerator can store a significant amount of food and beverages, making it suitable for larger households or individuals who prefer to do bulk shopping. The side-by-side design also offers the advantage of having both the refrigerator and freezer compartments at eye level, making it convenient to access frequently used items without bending down.
